150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20px; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: blue; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\">学员须知</span></strong> </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small\">亲爱的邮电的各位朋友：</span></span> </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small\">欢迎您参加拓展训练，为使这次培训获得圆满成功，请您仔细阅读以下条款：</span></span> </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">1. </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">穿着运动裤、运动鞋。请勿穿高跟鞋、裙子等服装。</span></span> </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">2. </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">学员有严重心脏病、高血压、腰椎方面疾病（或医生明确提醒不能够进行某种程度的运动）、习惯性扭伤、崴伤，不能参训；<span style=\"COLOR: red\">（重要）</span></span></span> </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">3. </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">如果学员在培训过程中有任何不适请立即告知带队培训师。<span style=\"COLOR: red\">（重要）</span></span></span> </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">4. </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">学员中如有少数民族，请注明是否有饮食方面禁忌；</span></span> </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">5.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">名单需提供给保险公司作为参训学员入保险之用，因此，姓名、性别、职务、身份证号码（护照号码）请务必填写正确并发传真和邮件；容易读音错误的多音字请帮忙注音；<span style=\"COLOR: red\">（重要）</span></span></span> </p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: small\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">6.</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">遵守公布给大家的时间流程安排和纪律。</span></span> </p><p></p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', '113', '学生处', '0102277', '学生处', '2014-10-28 15:40:29', '0102277', '高延春', '2014-10-28 15:40:24');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('swtzf9a81f0822334ab0', '', 'swtz', '0', '普通', '0', ';wsdx;', '中共重庆邮电大学委员会党校关于2014年秋季入党积极分子培训班开班的通知', '<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">校党委各直属党组织、各分党校：</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">经研究，学校党校2014年秋季入党积极分子培训班将于本周星期日开班，现将有关事项通知如下：</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0px 0px 0px 62px; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">1.</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">时间:2014年10月19日上午8：30。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0px 0px 0px 62px; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">2. </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">地点:第二国际会议厅（信科大厦二楼）。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 21px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">3.</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">请各学院负责对本单位参训学员进行集中动员培训，确保准时参加培训学习活动。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">4.</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">分党校组织的入党积极分子培训班由各分党校参照校党校的要求执行，具体方案报校党校备案。</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">附件：学员手册</span></p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><img style=\"VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; MARGIN-RIGHT: 2px\" src=\"http://222.177.140.105/system/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif\"/><a title=\"2014年秋季入党积极分子培训班学员手册.docx\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12px; COLOR: #0066cc\" href=\"/AttFile/file/20141030/1414632699781025496.docx\">2014年秋季入党积极分子培训班学员手册.docx</a></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\"></span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 35px; TEXT-INDENT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 中共重庆邮电大学委员会</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">党校</span></p><p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2014</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 19px; FONT-FAMILY: \" color:=\"\">年10月16日</span></p><p></p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', '113', '学生处', '0102277', '学生处', '2014-10-30 09:31:51', '0102277', '高延春', '2014-10-30 09:31:47');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('swtzfa61df27c61c4789', '', 'swtz', '0', '普通', '0', ';wsdx;', '关于认真学习贯彻习近平总书记在党的群众路线教育实践活动总结大会上重要讲话的通知', '<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 37px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 24px\">各党总支、各直属党支部：</span></span></p><p style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: auto; MARGIN-TOP: auto; LINE-HEIGHT: 40px; TEXT-INDENT: 43px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 24px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">&nbsp;10</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">月8日</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">，习近平总书记在党的群众路线教育实践活动总结大会上发表了重要讲话，全面总结了教育实践活动取得的新认识、积累的新经验，对巩固和拓展教育实践活动成果、切实增强全党同志爱党忧党兴党护党意识、加强党的作风建设、全面推进从严治党具有重要指导意义。认真学习贯彻习近平总书记重要讲话精神，是当前的一项重大政治任务。现将中共重庆市委教育工作委员会《关于认真学习贯彻习近平总书记在党的群众路线教育实践活动总结大会上重要讲话的通知》（渝教工委〔2014〕81号）（见附件）转发给你们，请按照通知要求，利用中心组学习和支部组织生活，认真学习《习近平总书记在党的群众路线教育实践活动总结大会上重要讲话》、《孙政才在全市党的群众路线教育实践活动总结大会上的讲话》。相关学习材料，请到党委宣传部网页上下载。</span></span></p><p style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: auto; MARGIN-TOP: auto; LINE-HEIGHT: 40px; TEXT-INDENT: 43px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 24px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><img style=\"VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; MARGIN-RIGHT: 2px\" src=\"http://222.177.140.105/system/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif\"/><a title=\"(2014)A634+关于认真学习贯彻习近平总书记在党的群众路线教育实践活动总结大会上重要讲话的通知_66493179[1].doc\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12px; COLOR: #0066cc\" href=\"/AttFile/file/20141030/1414632937291075075.doc\">(2014)A634+关于认真学习贯彻习近平总书记在党的群众路线教育实践活动总结大会上重要讲话的通知_66493179[1].doc</a></p><p style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: auto; MARGIN-TOP: auto; LINE-HEIGHT: 40px; TEXT-INDENT: 43px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 24px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: auto; MARGIN-TOP: auto; LINE-HEIGHT: 40px; TEXT-INDENT: 43px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 24px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\"></span></span></p><p style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: auto; MARGIN-TOP: auto; LINE-HEIGHT: 40px; TEXT-INDENT: 43px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 24px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">党委宣传部</span></span></p><p style=\"MARGIN-BOTTOM: auto; MARGIN-TOP: auto; LINE-HEIGHT: 40px; TEXT-INDENT: 43px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 24px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2014</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">年10月13日</span></span></p><p></p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', '113', '学生处', '0102277', '学生处', '2014-10-30 09:35:45', '0102277', '高延春', '2014-10-30 09:35:43');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('swtzfce6f78c-ef76-11e3-a783-474ca86607ee', 'wsdx', 'swtz', '0', '普通', '0', '', '重庆邮电大学', '<P>　一年一度的端午节之际，有的家庭通过包粽子，外出旅游来庆祝，然而，经济管理学院2013级信息管理与信息系统、电子商务、工程管理、物流管理等专业的学子们齐聚2117教室，举行“分享成长，携手进步，庆祝端午”班级、宿舍汇报活动，以示庆祝传统节日。 </P>\r\n<P>　首先，按照惯例，辅导员李海军老师进行了“端午节”假期结束返校情况清点工作，约有50人因为车程情况未能准时参加活动。 　　&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 其次，李老师结合发生在我们校友身边的两个案例给大家分享了举办班级、宿舍汇报交流活动的背景。作为大学毕业生，最起码的书面表达和口头表达以及简单的才艺能力还是必需具备的，否则很难适应用人单位的基本要求。</P>\r\n<P>　紧接着就是观摩了0311302班和0361302班以及18栋626、6栋206和1栋302同学带来的“分享成长，携手进步，庆祝端午”班级、宿舍汇报交流展演。才艺展示方面，时而声情并茂的朗诵，时而浑厚动听的歌声。此次活动是为了模仿学校先进班集体和五星文明寝室答辩，提升同学们的表达能力、合作分工能力以及丰富同学们的课余生活，引导同学们学会总结，学会分享。参与此次活动的宿舍是在申报创建先进班集体和五星文明寝室的候选单位中，各专业遴选的代表。来自信息管理与信息系统专业二班的班长亲自带队，为大家展示了班级建设的基本情况；来自电子商务专业2班的专业负责人罗娟带领5个小伙伴为大家从6个方面展示了成长与收获情况；18栋626、6栋206和1栋302三个宿舍的同学先后通过PPT为大家呈现了各自的特色与收获，他们都向观众推介了各自的成员，介绍了宿舍的收获与建设成果，同学们幽默诙谐的语言赢得了阵阵欢笑和掌声。 　　活动结束前，辅导员李海军老师邀请了4位同学对展示的5个集体的表现进行了点评。 </P>\r\n<P>　最后，李老师就近期的重点工作对大家进行了提醒和教育。 </P>', '0', '0', '', '待审核', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', '', '', '', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszx01713ac6-0037-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“文明宿舍之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323826955028728.png\" align=\"left\" style=\"width: 340px; height: 248px;\" alt=\"无标题.png\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323826955028728.png\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">百花齐放&nbsp;&nbsp;全面发展</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“文明宿舍之星”候选宿舍风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、集体简介</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">20栋808寝室，由通信与信息工程学院2010级4名女生组成。其中，中共党员1人、共青团员3人，3人报考北京邮电大学研究生已进入复试，1人签约成都芯通科技。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">团结友爱显真情。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">她们在生活上相互关心、学习上相互帮助</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">精神上相互鼓励</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">；她们共同制定学习计划、活动计划，合理规划大学生活；她们巾帼不让须眉，无论编程、仿真建模还是焊PCB板，她们都当仁不让、驾轻就熟。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">携手并肩共发展</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">大学</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">年，</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">她们CCT-2</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">过级率100%、</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">CET-4</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">过级率100%，</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">奖学金获得率100%，校优秀学生干部获评率100%，校优秀毕业生获评率100%，综合成绩排名全部位于专业前15%。寝室3人以初试高分入围北京邮电大学复试名单，1人签约成都芯通科技。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">重庆市文明寝室</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">，校</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">五星文明寝室2次</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">全国大学生数模竞赛市一等奖</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">人次</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">美国大学生数模</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">竞赛</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三等奖2人次</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">，重庆</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">市大学生艺术展演书法比赛三等奖1人次</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">，校级竞赛获奖</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2人次</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">国家励志奖学金4人</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">次，校</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">优秀学生奖学金</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">人次</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">、单项奖学金5人次；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">校级个人荣誉18人次。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、寝室格言</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">再长的路，一步步也能走完，再短的路，不迈开双脚也无法到达。</span></p><!--EndFragment--><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:44:48', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszx0912edb3-0036-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“特别奖”风采', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323742763062359.png\" align=\"left\" style=\"width: 402px; height: 248px;\" alt=\"无标题.png\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323742763062359.png\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>全面发展风华正茂&nbsp; 携手并进为校争光<br/>——第五届“五四之星”之“特别奖”风采<br/>一、“天才知道”团队成员简介</strong><br/>　　　朱芹，女，中共党员，通信与信息工程学院2011级通信与信息系统专业研究生，曾任校研究生会书记，现签约腾讯科技（深圳）有限公司。发表论文6篇（其中EI检索1篇，核心期刊1篇），获省部级及以上科技奖励6项，获奖学金9次，获校级及以上个人评优19次。&nbsp; <br/>　　　王晨星，女，共青团员，传媒艺术学院2011级广播电视编导专业学生，现任重庆邮电大学学生会副主席。获校级及以上个人评优10次，获校级及其以上文体比赛奖励14项。<br/>　　　陶秋屿，女，共青团员，外国语学院2012级商贸英语专业学生，现任外国语学院学生会副主席。获校级个人评优3次，还获得奖学金、配音大赛等奖项。<br/>　　　<strong>二、先进事迹<br/></strong>　　　势如破竹永攀高，巾帼出彩力压群雄。他们从2000余名学生参加的《天才知道》海选中，经过才艺展示、知识竞答等环节层层筛选，从100进20，再从20进8， 5名男生和3名女生突出重围组成重庆邮电大学代表队，赴中国教育电视台演播室录制《天才知道》专场复赛。在复赛中，8位选手以优异的表现为学校赢得了66500元的公益助学奖金。最终，朱芹、王晨星、陶秋屿3名同学晋级决赛，成为《天才知道》两个赛季以来首支全女生代表队。<br/>　　　披荆斩棘显风华，为校争光情系母校。作为西部唯一参赛高校团队，她们与来自清华大学、中山大学、中国人民大学、天津大学、北京交通大学、华东师范大学的选手们同台竞技。经过共答题、抢答题和风险推理题三轮紧张激烈角逐，她们以总分800分的优异成绩成功晋级半决赛。带着母校的嘱托，她们不畏强手，携手并进，在全国观众面前，尽显重邮学子的实力与风采，最终获得《天才知道》全国总决赛第五名。<br/><strong>四、团队格言</strong><br/>不要为自己找各种借口，除了你不优秀。</span></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 16pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span>&nbsp;</p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:44:42', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszx1f5f6b44-0038-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“才艺特长之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323646537010182.jpg\" align=\"left\" alt=\"8f66be31-0e3e-4ea4-bc48-3d5ec5694081.jpg\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323646537010182.jpg\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">手写音符&nbsp;&nbsp;朴实绘梦</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 26pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“才艺特长之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 20pt; text-indent: 44pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正仿宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 22pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">基本信息</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">张永晖，男，共青团员，传媒艺术学院2011级广播电视编导专业学生，现任学校大学生艺术团团长。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">组建乐队，改编演绎。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">他组建HOPE乐队并担任主唱，率队参加校“社团达人秀”、“黄桷馨声”草坪音乐会等节目演出；改编《乌苏里船歌》、《阿诗玛》、《茉莉花》等歌曲，创造性地将民歌用摇滚的方式展现出来。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">坚持原创，个性编排。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">他创办了“听者”原创音乐工作室，进行录音、MV、编曲等创作，并为第十八届校园十大歌手赛原创音乐进行录音及后期制作；工作室翻唱录制《可惜不是你》、《残酷月光》等作品的MV，并编排原创音乐剧“音为梦”；个人完成了《龙的传人》、《家》等的编曲。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">诠释好每一首歌，让音乐感染身边的每一个人，这是他最大的梦想。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2013年快乐男声重庆赛区（绿色通道）十强，重庆市雅居乐K歌大赛小组赛第一名；南岸区首届农民工歌手大赛二等奖，“我是飞young青春活出样”南岸区歌手大赛银奖，第三十一届“校园之春”歌手大赛南岸区第二名；校首届社团达人秀亚军，首届“邮人汇”才艺大赛最佳创意奖。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、座右铭</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">给我一个舞台、一只麦克风，我将舞出最真实的精彩。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:44:35', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszx360c0eaa-0037-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“健康运动之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323620919003978.png\" align=\"left\" alt=\"76988be0-28eb-4f66-bd07-27344b714f05.png\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323620919003978.png\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">用奔跑点燃的青春</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“健康运动之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、基本信息</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">高全利，男，共青团员，传媒艺术学院</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2011</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">级广播电视编导专业学生，现任传媒艺术学院田径队队长。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">坚持锻炼，运动改变人生。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一双跑鞋，一颗恒心，十二斤沙袋，滴滴汗水，成就了一个在奔跑中找回自信的他。三年前，缺乏运动、营养不良、体测不合格、生活学习不自信是他的真实写照；三年后，运动彻底改变了他的生活。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">积极带动，传递健康风尚。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">作为一名军训学员，他扛着院旗在拉练中鼓励同学走完</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">公里，整个途中他不停的奔跑呐喊，鼓舞队伍士气；作为编导专业学生，他发挥专业特长，完成第七届“青春杯”赛事相关视频制作，推广重邮体育精神；作为学院运动员，他打破学院</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">5000</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">米、</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">米纪录，并在校运会上获</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">5000</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">米第一名、</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">米第三名的好成绩；作为学院田径队队长，他积极组织队员训练，为学院在校运会上取得团体第四名的好成绩作出贡献；作为</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">年重庆国际马拉松比赛队员，他积极向身边的朋友宣传，组织百余人参赛，并带头坚持跑完全程。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">校运会</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">5000</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">米第一名</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">次，校运会</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">1500</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">米第三名</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">次；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">校优秀学生一等奖学金、二等奖学金；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三好学生等校级荣誉8项。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、座右铭</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">我运动！我健康！我快乐！</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:44:26', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszx45c94d43-0038-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“自立自强之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323594614068245.jpg\" align=\"left\" alt=\"7212e0ea-203f-4ee8-bed1-bdc450c68acc.jpg\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323594614068245.jpg\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">双拐撑起天空，自强走出人生</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 26pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“自立自强之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、基本信息</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">阮福亮，男，共青团员，软件学院2012级软件工程专业学生，现任班级科技委员。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">命运多舛，勇挑重担。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">他是一个身高只有1.1米，全身骨骼畸形的“小男孩”，12岁时，他经历了左肾坏死切除的痛苦。父亲去世，他与同样患有侏儒症的母亲和妹妹相依为命，用弱小的身躯支撑起家庭重担。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">坎坷求学，坚强自立。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2012年，在社会的资助下，他手杵双拐走进了重邮校园。左肾的切除，残疾的双腿，让他的精力和体力远不如常人。生活、学习中的一些常人认为简单不过的事情，对他来说往往要付出百倍的努力，哪怕是几分钟的路程对于杵着双拐的他来说都无比艰辛。关节的畸形让他坐立难安，双腿的无力让他艰难前行，腋下被拐杖磨出鲜血，可他却从未觉得自己和别人不一样：他总是能够按时上课，从不迟到；总是想办法独立解决生活中的困难，尽量不麻烦同学。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">穷且益坚，自强不息。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">他的梦想是毕业后成为一名软件工程师。为了赚取学费，他利用课余时间兼职重庆滨江皇冠假日酒店的微博管理工作，对此他很自豪，他说这是学以致用，他坚信只有坚持和付出才能创造自己的未来。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">重庆市自立自强先进个人；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">校自立自强先进个人、优秀共青团员、军训优秀学员；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">校春华秋实奖学金。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、座右铭</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">贫困不是放弃的借口，残疾不是懦弱的资本，疾病不是逃避的理由。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:44:20', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszx64246d6c-0037-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“自主创业之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323570531076711.png\" align=\"left\" style=\"width: 350px; height: 248px;\" alt=\"无标题.png\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323570531076711.png\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">挑战路激发创业梦</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“自主创业之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 20pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、主创人员信息</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">姜军，男，中共党员，经济管理学院</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">级管理科学与工程专业研究生，曾任校研究生会组织部部长、研究生院学生助理等，现任腾讯校园招聘</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">CRAT</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">团队队长。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">王健乐，男，中共党员，经济管理学院</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">级物流工程专业研究生，曾任校红十字会会长、校研究生会科技实践部副部长。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">志同道合，树立品牌。两位创始人相识于读研期间，二人立志共同打造“菜小二”品牌，让鲜果切消费成为快消时尚。“菜小二”于</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">年正式成立，以O</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">O形式专门制作校园鲜果切，在校内外有较高的影响力和知名度。团队为在校学生搭建了良好的实践平台，现有成员</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">余人</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">累计发放工资</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">万余元。目前拥有独立开发的官方网站（</span><a href=\"http://www.caixiao2.com/\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">www.caixiao2.com</span></a><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">）、微信公众平台和</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">App</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">软件，每月线上营业额</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">万余元；与华龙网、奇火锅及重庆部分高校均有合作协议，并不断推广。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">媒体报道，扩大影响。“菜小二”积极拓展业务领域，目前拥有“</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">Soft</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">软件研究院”和“零点零壹广告工作室”，并已为“菜小二”积累</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">万元发展资金。当前，“菜小二”团队创业事迹及“菜小二”品牌已被腾讯·大渝网（头版头条）、重庆新财经频道、网易、搜狐、新华网、大学生创业网和重庆晨报、商报等各大媒体广泛报道。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、团队奖项</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">GSVC</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">全球社会企业创业大赛三等奖；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">重庆市“农商行·诚易贷杯”第四届大学生创业大赛二等奖；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">重庆市弹子石CBD创业计划大赛铜奖。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 20pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、团队格言</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">立志二十年，做成一件事。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:44:13', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszx6754f20e-0038-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“勤奋好学之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323398370055162.jpg\" align=\"left\" alt=\"e00ffb07-b99c-4087-a710-2e45bdef0d61.jpg\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323398370055162.jpg\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">生命因拼搏而精彩&nbsp;&nbsp;人生因追求而美丽</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 26pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“勤奋好学之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 26pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、基本信息</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">肖颖，男，共青团员，光电工程学院2010级微电子学专业学生，曾任学习委员。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">专业中如鱼得水。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">他专业成绩、综合成绩四年来稳居年级第一(1/401)，获国家奖学金、长飞奖学金和春华秋实奖学金等各类奖学金6次，累计金额</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">28300</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">元；一次性通过CCT-2、CET-4、CET-6；被评为2012-2013学年度重庆市“三好学生标兵</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">，作为候选人参评2014年中国大学生年度人物。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">科研上勇攀高峰。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">科技创新丰富了他的大学生活：公开发表《新型高效放大器设计》和《高效LED电源设计》学术论文2篇；先后获得全国大学生电子设计竞赛模拟专题赛全国二等奖、美国数模竞赛国家二等奖等省部级及以上奖项7项；参与教育部人文社会科学研究《微博正能量唱响高校网络舆论主旋律》专项任务项目；成功申请校</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">大学生创新性实验计划项目</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">《DAB接收机固体无线更新系统》，现已顺利结题。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">未名湖书写未来。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">专业和科研的扎实基础坚定了他继续深造的想法，如今他以优异的成绩被录取为北京大学微电子与固体物理学专业硕士研究生。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">国家奖学金、长飞奖学金、春华秋实奖学金等6次；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">全国大学生电子设计竞赛模拟专题赛、美国数模竞赛国家二等奖等奖项7次；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">市三好学生标兵等荣誉10余次。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、座右铭</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">自强不息，厚德载物</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:44:07', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszx867b5685-0037-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“志愿奉献之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323376971097106.jpg\" align=\"left\" alt=\"a0ed66be-af00-4f05-a893-2409f9a7879c.jpg\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323376971097106.jpg\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">点滴奉献传递爱，持之以恒暖人心</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“志愿奉献之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、基本信息</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">彭志强，男，中共预备党员，光电工程学院2011级微电子学专业学生,现任院学生会副主席、青年志愿者服务队队长。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">回报社会关爱，温暖孤残老人。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">他是村里第一个“希望工程”受益者，爱心资助帮他圆梦大学。社会的帮助与关爱，他牢记于心，感恩于行：为了让失聪老人有机会重回有声世界，他连续5个小时在街头奔走呼吁，募集到助听器善款3000余元；为了关爱孤寡老人，他3年坚持到敬老院、社区开展志愿服务，为30多位老人带去了亲人般的温暖。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">传递爱与希望，扶助求学儿童。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">为了帮助酉阳娄底小学的孩子们，他通过组织20位同学义演，筹到3000元善款；通过3天社区募捐，筹集100余件衣物；通过4次校外资源协调，征集300余本书籍。看着那73名小学生充满希望的眼神，一如看到儿时的自己。为了提高农民工子女学习成绩，他先后组织216名志愿者开展南坪“阳光公寓”义教活动，为20多名农民工子女提供67次辅导，历时200余小时。为了关爱留守儿童，他组织了“同心铜梦”三下乡志愿行，和队员节省生活费1000余元，购买一批文具，赠送给铜梁太平镇的60名留守儿童。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">以志愿服务践行雷锋精神，他是受益者，也是接班人。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 22pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖状况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">“青年人·中国梦”全国大学生社会实践优秀团队（队长）；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">市青年志愿者先进个人标兵、市青年志愿者先进个人、“云博会”优秀志愿者、市“节用惜福”优秀志愿者；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">优秀学生干部等校级获奖10项。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 22pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、座右铭</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">勿以善小而不为</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:44:01', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszx8cfa28c7-0038-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“孝老敬亲之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323353727004804.jpg\" align=\"left\" alt=\"606d845d-4c37-4866-8d5d-dcf6436cd335.jpg\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323353727004804.jpg\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">坚强，承担，用行动注解孝德</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“孝老敬亲之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、基本信息</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">蔡长兴，男，中共预备党员，法学院2011级法学专业学生，曾任法学院团总支宣传部副部长，现任校学生处助理。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">拳拳孝举</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">，跪乳反哺。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">父亲从小患上小儿麻痹症，离开拐杖就不能独立行走；母亲个子矮小，又是聋哑残疾人。从10岁起，他便承担了小到扫地、煮饭，大到耕田、种地的家庭劳务。在他15岁那年的夏天，父亲瘫痪了，生活不能自理，他毅然回家照顾父亲，给父亲喂饭、洗脸、洗澡、剃胡须，抱着父亲上厕所。白天，他扛着锄头下地干活；晚上彻夜守在父亲床前，为的就是在父亲偶然疼醒的时候能够喂一口开水。半年之后，父亲能说话了，他也在社会各方的支持下重返校园。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">心系父母，坚强担当。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">进入大学以后，他肩上的担子更重了。为了偿还父亲治病欠下的债务，他最多的时候要同时做4份兼职，还需经常回家做家务、干农活和照看父母。距离再远，事情再多，父母永远是他生命里最重要的部分，无论多么辛苦，他始终微笑面对各种困境，坚强支撑着整个家庭，因为他知道，承担，才是他生活下去不变的选择，奋斗才会创造出理想的人生。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2012年度中国大学生自强之星提名奖。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、座右铭</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">对自己好点，因为一辈子不长；对身边的人好点，因为下辈子不一定能够遇见！</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:43:55', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszxae42382c-0038-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“党员模范之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323325767007622.jpg\" align=\"left\" alt=\"fcc9d598-06ba-4b79-976b-9ccb1fb5baa5.jpg\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323325767007622.jpg\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">平凡中显不平凡</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">实干中彰显品质</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">第五届&nbsp;“五四之星”之“党员模范之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 26pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、基本信息</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">王斌，男，中共预备党员，通信与信息工程学院</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">级通信工程专业</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">0111002</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">班学生，曾任楼长、舍长、校宿管会会长。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">默默奉献，事无巨细。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">大一作为宿管会干事和楼长每周辗转奔波在各个寝室楼栋检查寝室卫生，重复、单调，从不抱怨。大二任男生宿舍</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">栋舍长期间，第一个以“宿管报”形式传达活动、通知，第一个实施楼栋成员档案管理规范制；在其带领下</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">栋以全校基础分第一，答辩分第一的成绩获得校“五星文明楼”称号。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">勇于担当，勤奋务实。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">大三竞聘为第一届学生宿舍自我管理与服务委员会会长。作为转型成长期宿管会的干部，完善队伍、规范制度、丰富活动，使队伍从小到大，制度从无到有、活动从单一到丰富。第一届“最美宿管阿姨评选”、</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">第一届“旧书换盆栽”活动等深受欢迎，规范的管理、高效的服务，创新的活动，被亲切的称为“王管家”。大四作为毕业生不再担任宿管干部，但仍协助负责本年级寝室卫生，开展学院公寓区文化建设工作。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">平凡岗位，踏实前行。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">做好一件事情不难，难的是一件事坚持</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">1300</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">多天。作为学校第一批研究生支教团</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">名成员之一，他将继续发扬实干奉献的精神坚持走下去。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">重庆市优秀学生干部，重庆市三下乡优秀团队；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">校优秀学生干部</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">次，校优秀学生奖学金</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">次，其他各类荣誉奖项8项。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、座右铭</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">对于明天最好的准备就是将今天做得最好！</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:43:49', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszxc76d48e4-0036-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“优秀班级之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323298067070574.jpg\" align=\"left\" style=\"width: 353px; height: 248px;\" alt=\"dcddd6bb-4713-4c61-a7f9-58936c5d9017.jpg\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323298067070574.jpg\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">因为梦想所以拼搏&nbsp;&nbsp;因为拼搏所以优秀</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“优秀班级之星”候选班级风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、集体简介</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">0491101班，来自计算机科学与技术学院2011级计算机科学与技术专业，共33人，其中中共党员7人。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">班级建设共谋划。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">秉承“班级是我家，建设靠大家”的理念，班团干部和党员带头组织开展政治学习；定期开展班会交流，各抒己见，商定发展目标，发挥主观能动性。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">学风优良齐进步。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">学习上狠抓基础、注重效率，以交流合作促个性发展；采用自选科研导师定向指导、实践分享式轻松学习等方式，变“要我学”为“我要学”；成立考研小组和就业小组，信息共享，互帮互助。截至大三上学期，全班奖学金覆盖率100%，课程通过率100%，平均绩点3.49，补考率和重修率均为零；CCT2一次性过级率100%，CET4一次性过级率100%且平均分510.12分，CET6过级率84%。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">全面发展重实践。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">班级成员全面发展，积极参加科技活动，勇于投身社会实践，热心市民学校、志愿班级、敬老爱老等社团活动和志愿服务。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">重庆市先进班集体标兵；校先进班集体、校十佳五四红旗团支部、校五四红旗团支部；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">市文明寝室一间、市三好学生1人次、市科技创新先进个人2人次；校级各类个人荣誉62人次；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">获奖学金62人次、共113500元；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">各类竞赛获国家级奖3人次、省部级奖27人次、校级奖30余人次。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、班级格言</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">因为梦想，所以拼搏；因为拼搏，所以优秀！&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:43:43', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszxc9af7fb2-0037-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“网络建设之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323252180015174.jpg\" align=\"left\" alt=\"62744b7d-5d63-487d-b196-4ee9abe1e09d.jpg\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323252180015174.jpg\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">E想天开，脚踏实地</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“网络建设之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、基本信息</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">蒋子良，男，共青团员，经济管理学院2011级市场营销专业学生，现任“红岩网校”工作站站长。</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、先进事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">脚踏实地，服务师生。</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">他先后参与了学校“党的群众路线教育实践活动”、“天才知道”、“学业辅导中心”等23个重点网站的建设工作，组织开展了100余场网络建设知识培训。他依托新媒体技术，与团队研发“重邮小帮手”微信平台，通过拓展“教务资讯查询”功能，目前粉丝达13000多人，日均请求量超5000次，已成为重邮校园生活学习的好帮手。</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">创新发展，成就梦想。</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">在他和“红岩网校</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">”</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">工作站其他同学的共同努力下，“红岩网校”获评第六届“全国高校百佳网站”；“中国梦·我的梦”主题教育网站荣获全国优秀“我的中国梦”活动专题特别奖。此外，他与团队共同完成的作品《让高校主题网站“e展‘红’图”——基于“红岩网校”等主题网站的调查分析》荣获第十三届“挑战杯”竞赛累进创新金奖。</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">“红岩网校”获评“全国高校百佳网站”，</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">“<span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">中国梦</span></span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">·</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">我的梦<span style=\"font-family: 仿宋;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">主题教育网站</span></span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">荣获全国优秀“我的中国梦”活动专题特别奖；</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">第十三届“挑战杯”竞赛累进创新金奖；全国市场营销策划大赛重庆赛区二等奖；</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">重庆市三下乡先进个人；校中天科技奖学金。</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、座右铭</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">世界因你不同</span><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:43:37', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('wszxf641bc28-0037-11e4-b41f-08edb9d851b3', 'wsdx', 'wszx', '0', '普通', '0', '', '第五届“五四之星”之“科技创新之星”', '<p>	</p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img width=\"177\" height=\"248\" title=\"1410323186948082197.jpg\" align=\"left\" alt=\"c0459cd6-b503-459d-a016-99da86a9ed8e.jpg\" src=\"/AttFile/image/20140910/1410323186948082197.jpg\" hspace=\"12\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">追梦挑战，努力到底</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><!--?xml:namespace prefix=\"o\" ns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\"--><o:p></o:p><!--?xml:namespace--></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">——第五届“五四之星”之“科技创新之星”候选人风采</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">一、基本信息</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">叶升蔚，男，中共党员，马克思主义学院2013级马克思主义理论专业研究生，曾任“重邮e站”手机报首任主编、腾讯校园招聘助理等7项职务。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">二、主要事迹</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">潜心科研出成绩。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">他</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">在</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">本科期间以第一作者身份发表学术论文4篇，目前参研重庆市社科规划课题1项。他连续两届担任</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">队长</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">参加“挑战杯”竞赛，在2013年的第十三届“挑战杯”竞赛中，其团队作品成为全国决赛教育类6件优秀作品之一，他率队参加答辩，最终荣获全国二等奖。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">依托新媒勇创新。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">他组建重邮第一支互联网产品团队“PMbird”，参加2013年“人人网”校园开发者大赛获西南区第四名，受邀参加虎嗅F&amp;M年度论坛，与搜狗CEO王小川、虎嗅网</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">CEO李岷</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">等互联网公司高层进行交流。先后开发运营网站、微信公众平台7个，其中“考研狗”微信公众平台，上线后3天，关注量即破千。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三、获奖情况</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">第十三届“挑战杯”全国大学生课外学术科技作品竞赛全国二等奖；2013腾讯</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">西南区</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">优秀</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">CRAT团队</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">；2013“人人网”开发者大赛西南区第四名；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">重庆市优秀学生干部、重庆市优秀志愿者；</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">“五四之星”提名</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">奖</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">三好学生</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">优秀学生</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">干部</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">等</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">校级</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">奖项</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">20余</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">次</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">四、座右铭</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;方正小标宋_GBK&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\">将梦想进行到底，将努力进行到底。</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;仿宋_GB2312&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"p0\" style=\"line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 28pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment--><p>\r\n	</p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', 'admin', '重庆邮电大学', '2014-10-16 09:43:31', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('xgxz2d2c1ac3f1a145d5', 'wsdx', 'xgxz', '0', '普通', '0', '', '重庆邮电大学本科学生党员“两薄一书”填写参考模板', '<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 16px\"><img style=\"VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; MARGIN-RIGHT: 2px\" src=\"http://222.177.140.105/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_rar.gif\"/><a title=\"重庆邮电大学党员“两簿一书”填写参考模板20140507.rar\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12px; COLOR: #0066cc\" href=\"/AttFile/file/20141023/1414025897218087512.rar\">重庆邮电大学党员“两簿一书”填写参考模板20140507.rar</a></p><p></p>', '0', '0', '', '已发布', '0', '', '113', '学生处', '0102277', '学生处', '2014-10-23 08:59:12', '0102277', '高延春', '2014-10-23 08:59:08');
INSERT INTO `t_sys_notic` VALUES ('xgxz6956f897-e706-11e3-bdba-9f0537098684', 'wsdx', 'xgxz', '0', '普通', '0', '', '重庆邮电大学共青团2013', '　一年一度的端午节之际，有的家庭通过包粽子，外出旅游来庆祝，然而，经济管理学院2013级信息管理与信息系统、电子商务、工程管理、物流管理等专业的学子们齐聚2117教室，举行“分享成长，携手进步，庆祝端午”班级、宿舍汇报活动，以示庆祝传统节日。  \r\n　　首先，按照惯例，辅导员李海军老师进行了“端午节”假期结束返校情况清点工作，约有50人因为车程情况未能准时参加活动。  \r\n　　其次，李老师结合发生在我们校友身边的两个案例给大家分享了举办班级、宿舍汇报交流活动的背景。作为大学毕业生，最起码的书面表达和口头表达以及简单的才艺能力还是必需具备的，否则很难适应用人单位的基本要求。  \r\n　　紧接着就是观摩了0311302班和0361302班以及18栋626、6栋206和1栋302同学带来的“分享成长，携手进步，庆祝端午”班级、宿舍汇报交流展演。才艺展示方面，时而声情并茂的朗诵，时而浑厚动听的歌声。此次活动是为了模仿学校先进班集体和五星文明寝室答辩，提升同学们的表达能力、合作分工能力以及丰富同学们的课余生活，引导同学们学会总结，学会分享。参与此次活动的宿舍是在申报创建先进班集体和五星文明寝室的候选单位中，各专业遴选的代表。来自信息管理与信息系统专业二班的班长亲自带队，为大家展示了班级建设的基本情况；来自电子商务专业2班的专业负责人罗娟带领5个小伙伴为大家从6个方面展示了成长与收获情况；18栋626、6栋206和1栋302三个宿舍的同学先后通过PPT为大家呈现了各自的特色与收获，他们都向观众推介了各自的成员，介绍了宿舍的收获与建设成果，同学们幽默诙谐的语言赢得了阵阵欢笑和掌声。  \r\n　　活动结束前，辅导员李海军老师邀请了4位同学对展示的5个集体的表现进行了点评。  \r\n　　最后，李老师就近期的重点工作对大家进行了提醒和教育。   ', '0', '0', '', '待审核', '0', '', 'cqupt', '重庆邮电大学', '', '', '', 'admin', '管理员', '2014-09-08 11:39:15');
